   Geico 400 - Practice

   Brian France (from left), chairman & CEO of NASCAR, Mike Helton,
   president of NASCAR, and Robin Pemberton, NASCAR Vice President, hold a
   press conference following a meeting with drivers for the NASCAR Sprint
   Cup Series at Chicagoland Speedway. (Sean Gardner / Getty Images /
   September 14, 2013)
